Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫木之本櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今年春天開始 升入了友枝中學的國一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然還是很不擅長數學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是我每天都努力學習和參加社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}十分忙碌又快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.89,biaoti,,0,0,0,,小櫻和兔子和月亮之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然櫻花已經謝了 不過還是很美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和大家一起賞花好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且小狼也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真好真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.83,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}賞花真好啊 我也好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可 你不應該留在家裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我都忍著沒去賞花了 這次就讓我出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不是吃了很多特產點心 很滿足的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個是那個 這個是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只有知世和小狼倒是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 轉學生也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}上次的特產點心就是秋穗送的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 她是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有啊 大家吃完便當之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世還唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的很好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早知道就拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你帶了手機的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}唱完之後我才想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是有一種東西 在想著「就是現在」的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就能立刻開始拍照或錄影就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣的話 我的帥氣姿勢也就全部能拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可你也拿到了手機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世媽媽的公司好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不光是玩具 還賣手機和電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}耳機也做得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你就知道用它打遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下次一定要戰勝斯比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你出門有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 出來買晚飯要用的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是我才剛搬過來 不知道要去哪裡買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一直都是你出來買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是 是和我一起住的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很重要的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 那個人也不是每次都有空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以我就想盡量幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟我只會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你果然很喜歡那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好可愛的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我一直都帶著它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 不知道能不能帶到學校去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}賞花的時候我也想帶上來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是怕你們覺得我幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們學校可以帶玩偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家一定都會覺得很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是 一直都和小可…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那 那個 是這樣的 我一直都很珍惜一個叫小可的玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和我一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明天開始 我也帶它一起去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我 我也帶上 和小可一起去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}它有沒有名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有的 叫小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小桃你好 我叫小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我才是 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是吧 小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你回來啦 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你回來了啊 不去大學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}晚上還要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我現在是回來拿資料的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我回來了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你去買東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 今天我做晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天吃馬鈴薯奶汁烤菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有雞蛋燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那是用來做便當的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.75,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}{\an7}藤隆  大概5點回家 我到時候發簡訊 \N桃矢  放學後要打工 在家吃晚飯 \N小櫻  4點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 大家都寫了回家時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我回來晚了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這倒沒關係 你是有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}碰到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們一起買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是那個轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是你說去過很多個國家的轉學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}莓鈴 你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你還是一點沒變啊 木之本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}表情呆呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你那邊沒事嗎 是不是要準備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}香港現在幾點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之前跟你說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}比你們晚一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我正在悠閒地吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真好啊 桃包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這小丫頭還是一點沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你才是 還是那麼小隻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我這哪裡小了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你給我看好了 這帥氣的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太大了 礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}混蛋丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}確 確實有點礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼連小櫻都這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個礙事的玩偶先放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.67,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}別放一邊啊 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}別無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然他說在安定下來之前先不加入社團
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是學校還是很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那當然有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還在某人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你還真是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟是小櫻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看來小狼還得繼續辛苦下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小丫頭你不來這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也要上學 所以不能馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但我打算暑假的時候去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要給我帶路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}去好玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會好好調教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給我做好準備吧 小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我可是會反擊的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 下次再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以見到莓鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也告訴知世一聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}去哪裡好呢 去她沒去過的地方比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}到時一定要好好拍下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}爸爸 你吃完飯就要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 應該要住在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真是忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟要準備學術研討會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有第一次發表論文的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也想盡全力幫他們看看論文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要注意身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝關心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}經典失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}拍下來作紀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.11,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.49\pos(252,122)\fad(651,0)}給雪兔看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥就知道欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你有什麼想對我說的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你是想要我的鑰匙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}鍾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只是和你說話你也不回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不好意思啊 好像在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我再去切一點麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為昨天和秋穗約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和秋穗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣啊 所以才帶上了小可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可也不小 放在包外面還是挺顯眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就算這樣 這又是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然我覺得比手機還大的吊墜有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可真是單純
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}遠方的綠波滾滾沸騰 成暗紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大船也發出震耳欲聾的聲響奮力直追
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}卻總是追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}某天 我叫住一個船上的男子問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「這艘船是在往西行嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}男子詫異地看了我一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後反問我 「為什麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「因為看起來好像在追落日」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的 到這裡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你的朗讀 木之本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就像這樣 「夢十夜」就是寫了關於夢的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}裡面全是不可思議的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也有人會覺得可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有 有一種叫「預知夢」的夢境 大家知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是夢到未來發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}預知夢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.52,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個「夢十夜」並不是預知夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個夢到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然之前也夢到過觀月老師和艾利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那麼詩之本同學 你接著念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}男子呵呵笑了起來 然後徑自走遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「西沉之日的盡頭是東邊嗎 那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}東升之日的源頭是西邊嗎 那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}身在浪上 以櫓為枕 漂吧漂吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天我帶了自己做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你讀得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道我有沒有讀對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}讀得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你決定好去哪個社團了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我還在糾結中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}友枝中學還有戲劇部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你剛剛讀得那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}奈緒子也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們兩位是拉拉隊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 你也想試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我之前沒試過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事的 很多人都是國中才加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}合唱隊你感興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}如果你現在沒有急事 請一定要跟我們一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我去向老師申請過了 午休借用這個教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你在賞花的時候不是一起唱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我聽到你在一起哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}美妙通靈的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}擾亂了你的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以的話 在這裡一起唱唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但 但是 我沒怎麼在人前唱過歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可能唱得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}唱吧唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.38,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}朧月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗 你知道這首歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在學習日語的時候學過這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能拜託你來伴奏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我聽說你彈得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}莓鈴說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼你會彈鋼琴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}彈得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是害你沒唱好也不關我事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只有我們聽到真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}都是多虧了知世同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是因為你唱得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}伴奏非常合拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就決定去合唱隊好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我還想聽你和知世的二重唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}如果不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家一定會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想進合唱隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}熱烈歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我還是頭一次聽這麼好聽的朧月夜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 拉拉隊的練習結束得早的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我就去合唱隊參觀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然不知道 但有什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大道寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這間教室還可以繼續用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我借了一整個中午 所以還能用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我有點事情 可以借用一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗 我們去領入部申請表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}現在去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他們好像有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聲音是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}昨天晚飯的時候就聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聽上去好像在吱吱響 好像在哪聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世以前使用過的攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 從哪傳來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}隱藏著夢之力量的鑰匙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在我面前顯示你真正的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無主之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「RECORD」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「記錄」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又是一張新的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我什麼也沒感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和庫洛牌的時候完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我什麼也沒有感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.01,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.21,0:24:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這裡是必看的「交給小可」環節
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次介紹大家都很喜歡的戰鬥服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個就是捕獲「行動」卡牌時穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}日本風與中國風的絕妙搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}桃和蓮的圖案是點睛之筆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.49,0:24:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說起桃子 以前有個傢伙吃桃子惹怒了神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:31.49,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}悟空!? 你見過嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.13,0:24:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}像猴子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.37,0:24:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是那小鬼鋼琴彈得那麼好 還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.77,0:24:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也不能認輸 必須想一個必殺技才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.72,0:24:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.53,0:24:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世邀請我去她家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.42,0:24:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還讓我看了新的攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.23,0:24:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很小但很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.64,0:24:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下集 和小櫻在院子裡捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.79,0:24:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和小櫻一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.23,0:24:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}
